flowchart LR
    subgraph Spryker["🛒 Scania Service Shop (Spryker)"]
        Yves["Yves Storefront"]
        Modules["Scania Integration Modules<br><small>Client + Zed connectors</small>"]
        OMSc["OMS Commands<br><small>post-order async</small>"]
        Mail["OOTB Mailer"]
    end

    CIAM["🔐 CIAM (My Scania)"]
    FMAT["🚛 FMAT"]
    SECM["📋 SECM"]
    SPISA["📦 PIM-SPISA"]
    SMTP["📧 SMTP"]

    Yves -- "SSO login · OAuth2/OIDC · sync · every login · POC" --> CIAM
    CIAM -- "profile, company, roles, products · REST · sync · POC" --> Yves
    Modules -- "fetch assets · REST · sync · on asset page (paginated) · POC" --> FMAT
    Modules -- "fetch services + prices · REST · sync · after asset select (~100/veh) · POC" --> SECM
    Modules -- "fetch service details · REST · sync · on service select · POC" --> SPISA
    OMSc -- "order created · REST · async (OMS) · per order · POC" --> FMAT
    OMSc -. "payment + activation date · REST · async (OMS) · per order · FUTURE" .-> FMAT
    Mail -- "order confirmation · SMTP · push · per order · POC" --> SMTP

